      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a distinguished example of automotive excellence, maintained to a high standard of mechanical and aesthetic integrity. This vehicle offers a refined driving experience, characterized by a responsive powertrain and a well-preserved interior cabin. Each component has been thoroughly vetted to ensure continued performance and reliability. This offering represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a superior balance of sophistication and value.",
      "price": 32500.0,
